  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `WorkspaceAiService.cs:41-44` — locate the hardcoded GUID.</step>
    <step order="2">Trace the GUID to its Dataverse playbook (use MCP `read_query` on `sprk_analysisplaybook` filtered by `sprk_analysisplaybookid`) to resolve which stable code to bind (`summarize-new-files` vs `document-profile` vs other).</step>
    <step order="3">Document the resolved code in `notes/handoffs/018-aisummary-code-decision.md`.</step>
    <step order="4">Update `WorkspaceOptions.AiSummaryPlaybookCode` default to the resolved code; update matching `appsettings.Development.json` key. (Scope: value-only — do NOT add new properties.)</step>
    <step order="5">Refactor `WorkspaceAiService.cs`: inject `IOptions&lt;WorkspaceOptions&gt;` + `IPlaybookLookupService`; replace hardcoded GUID with `await _playbookLookup.GetByCodeAsync(_options.Value.AiSummaryPlaybookCode, tenantId, ct)`.</step>
    <step order="6">Verify public contract unchanged.</step>
    <step order="7">Update unit tests with stable code fixtures.</step>
    <step order="8">Add integration test asserting end-to-end summarize flow.</step>
    <step order="9">Run `dotnet build` + `dotnet test`. Pass.</step>
    <step order="10">Measure publish size; report delta.</step>
    <step order="11">Run code-review + adr-check (Step 9.5 FULL gates).</step>
    <step order="12">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 018 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
